- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the use of autonomous robots for excavation tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of Artificial Neural Tissue (ANT) as a control approach for the robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of control approaches for coordinating the actions of multiple robots. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the development of software for controlling the robots. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of multiple autonomous robots working together.
